        <item>
          <text><![CDATA[<p><b><b>Centralized Opioid Guidance Act of 2018 or the COG Act of 2018</b></b></p> <p>This bill requires the Centers for Medicare &amp; Medicaid Services to publish and periodically update all guidance issued since January 1, 2016, related to the prescription of opioids for Medicare beneficiaries.</p>]]></text>
